## New project setup — quick checklist

1. Duplicate theme folder → rename to client name
2. Update style.css theme header
3. Swap font @imports in style.css Section 1a + 1b
4. Update --font-body and --font-heading in :root
5. Update color tokens in :root — ACF color picker palette syncs automatically from style.css, no secondary update needed
6. Mirror all token changes in theme.json
7. Import ACF field groups via ACF → Tools → Import
8. Add brand overrides in style.css Section 10
9. Remove test fonts (Section 1d + Section 8c) when fonts chosen
10. Remove unused blocks and templates
11. Push to staging and verify

